<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="page-title" style="color: #895bac;">
        Contact Us
      </div>

      <div class="message">
        DMC welcomes cooperation and partnership in order to better serve as a public platform for developers, 
        service providers, and end-users. <br />For any inquiries or support, please contact us.
      </div>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt contact-icon"></i>
        아주대학교 산학원 534호 분산이동통신 연구실 / Ajou Univ. San-Hak-Won no.534, Distributed Mobile Computing Lab.
        <br>
        <i class="fas fa-phone-alt contact-icon"></i>
        031-219-1897 (교내 1897)
        <br>
        <i class="fas fa-envelope contact-icon"></i>
        saarc@ajou.ac.kr
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="map" style="width: 100%; height: 400px;"></div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=0235628b64829606c7f0ff1c4ff412ca"></script>
    <script>
      var container = document.getElementById('map'); //지도를 담을 영역의 DOM 레퍼런스

      var options = { //지도를 생성할 때 필요한 기본 옵션
        center: new kakao.maps.LatLng(37.28305700556231, 127.04366229466967), //지도의 중심좌표.
        level: 3 //지도의 레벨(확대, 축소 정도)
      };

      
      var map = new kakao.maps.Map(container, options); //지도 생성 및 객체 리턴

      var markerPosition  = new kakao.maps.LatLng(37.28305700556231, 127.04366229466967); 
      var marker = new kakao.maps.Marker({
          position: markerPosition
      });
      marker.setMap(map);

    </script>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  </body>
</html>


<style>
  .message{
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 40px;
    text-align: justify;
    font-weight: 200;
    padding-right: 40px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .contact-icon{
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  .contact-info{
    margin-top: 100px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 200;
    line-height: 40px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 812px) {
    .message{
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 34px;
      text-align: justify;
      padding-right:0px;
    }

    .contact-info{
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 200;
      line-height: 34px;
    }

  }


</style>


